			"content": {
				"number": "4",
				"title": "Barnvacciner som kan förskrivas på beredskapslicens",
				"id": "c1c_51",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>L&auml;kemedelsnamn</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Vaccin</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\">Enskild eller generell licens beh&ouml;ver ej s&ouml;kas f&ouml;r vacciner till&shy;g&auml;ngliga via beredskapslicens f&ouml;r kompletterande vaccina&shy;tion enligt nationellt program till barn. Vid annan vaccinering ans&ouml;ks om enskild eller generell licens p&aring; det lokala apoteket.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Difterivaccin SSI 30 IE/dos (25 Lf/dos)</p>\r\n<p>Obs! En dos = 0,5 ml</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>D</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Difterivaccin SSI&nbsp;2 IE/dos (6,25 Lf/dos)</p>\r\n<p>Obs! En dos = 0,5 ml</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>D</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Tetanusvaccin SSI</p>\r\n<p>Obs! En dos = 1 ml</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>T</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>"
